onExitReport(ExitReport) - Method in class launcher.watchdog.EngineWatchdog
Handles exiting of program when an ExitReport is submitted.

Called by EngineWatchdog.start() when EngineWatchdog.exitReport becomes non-null, signifying the program wants to exit.

Logs the ExitReport, and then calls either ExitHandler.onExit(ExitReport) on EngineWatchdog.exitHandler, or CrashHandler.onCrash(CrashReport) on EngineWatchdog.crashHandler, depending on the value of ExitReport.isClean(), to handle the report accordingly.
